subject: Dear Beneficiary,
body:
Dear Beneficiary,
My name is Mrs Lilia Nichole, I am a store keeper with Custom department at
John Kennedy Airport United State of America. I discover an abandon consignment
in your name and address. If you are interested in your claim let me
know so that i can hand it over to reliable diplomatic agent to
deliver it to you, after the delivery you can settle me 5%, because i
discover that the consignment is loaded with money.
Reply Asap
Mrs Lilia Nichole

subject: Re:   Dear Beneficiary,
body:
Dear Mrs. Lilia Nichole,

Thank you for your message. I am intrigued by your discovery and would like to know more about this abandoned item that is apparently in my name and address. Could you please provide more details about it? 

Looking forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Sidney
